title: My games were super competitive and hard in ranked.... but then...
body:
all the sudden every enemy turned into bronze V... i've won my last 7 ranked games just kinda dicking around.... LIKE WTF?

i just hear the keshaway songs rolling through my head as the games are going on.... it is sad...

like who tf invades at lvl 1, then has 3 teammates die? how do 3 people die at level ONE? 3 for zero..... like lol okay, ty for the win
